 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
