.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, juice, milk
House: tower, colonial, modern, futuristic, craftsman
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, house, reggae
5 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, mouse, pony, rabbit
 1. the colonial house is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the fan of country##1
 5. the tower house is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the colonial house is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the tower house##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the craftsman house##1
12. the modern house is the fan of house##1
13. the craftsman house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| House   | modern  | futuristic | colonial | tower  | craftsman  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | country    | blues        | reggae | folk     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

